node.text:
I shrank and met the Broodmother aka the demon orb weaver! She was not very happy about my visit, but then I built a parkour run for my other little friends who were friendlier and happier about it. Have you heard about Grounded? Grounded is a cooperative survival-adventure game where the players are shrunk to the size of an ant and have to explore, build and survive together in a vibrant and dangerous backyard. Full Parkour video with more information about the new update coming to Grounded on my YouTube channel InsecthausTV. 

@Obsidian #xbox #sponsored
